title: We Finally Landed Our Dream Guest... - Off The Rails #38
description: Today may be the most Off the Rails episode of Off the Rails we've ever done. First, we FINALLY have a call with the incomparable Wali P! Then the train completely leaves the tracks when Jimmie Lee the Jersey Outlaw calls in with the most deranged interaction imaginable. Jump into it!
